reviewText: There should me more teacher involved and more professional way should be done, not like powerpoint.

Enjoyed this course and learned a lot; Especially on strategic planning aspect.  A couple of things to note: The first quiz did not reflect the material of Week 1 and instructions on the Strategic Planning Agenda assignment lacked clarity on the expectation of the end result.
Thank you! I want to express my gratitude to the teachers who made such a useful and necessary course!
It's a very good course which can help you understand the basic konwledge about business!!  recommend！
